  "description": "<p>Specification</p>\n <p>Product Information</p>\n <p>Item Code:N604D892425S</p>\n <p>Product Type :Combo Item</p>\n <p>Product Name:Metal bed, 3FT single bed 90x190cm, With LED light strip and 4 drawerss, 2 USB port+1 Type C, Durable and Sturdy, Youth bed, for adults &amp; teenagers, Multifunctional bed, Wrought iron bed, Grey</p>\n <p>Place of Origin:China</p>\n <p>Main Color:Gray</p>\n <p>Main Material:MDF+Metal</p>\n <p>Bed Size:90cm*190cm</p>\n <p>Product Dimensions</p>\n <p>Assembled Length (cm):207.00</p>\n <p>Assembled Width (cm):90.50</p>\n <p>Assembled Height (cm):105.00</p>\n <p>Product Weight (kg):34.00</p>\n <p>Package Size</p>\n <p>Sub-item 1: N604P178925SPackage Quantity: 1111 * 18.01 * 16 cm 15 kg</p>\n <p>Sub-item 2: N604P178924SPackage Quantity: 1111 * 38.51 * 16.99 cm 23 kg</p>\n <p>Product Features</p>\n <ul>\n  <li>High-quality materials: Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, this bed boasts a robust metal frame that promises steadfast durability, ensuring it stands the test of time.</li>\n  <li>Designed with 4 drawers: Underbed drawers are fitted with castors for effortless pushing and pulling. Maximize your storage potential without compromising on style. The thoughtfully designed built-in drawers offer ample space to tuck away clutter, freeing up valuable floor area and keeping your room clutter-free.</li>\n  <li>USB charging ports: 3 charging ports are thoughtfully prepared at the bedside, including two 2 Type-A and one Type-C, 5V / 2A.</li>\n  <li>Bedside design with light strips: The light strip can be adjusted with three levels of brightness and a variety of colours, and can be controlled by mobile app and Bluetooth. Elevate your sleep experience with the integrated LED light strip, casting a warm and inviting glow over your resting space. This modern touch not only illuminates your surroundings but also adds a touch of elegance to the overall design, making it a true statement piece.</li>\n  <li>Minimalist styling: Effortlessly blending into a range of interior decors, this versatile bed is a must-have for homeowners who appreciate both comfort and aesthetics. Its rustic wood finish imparts a cozy charm, enhancing the ambiance and creating a warm and welcoming environment.</li>\n  <li>Easy to Install: Detailed instructions and complete parts are available to help you complete the assembly. The fun of installation makes you enjoy the bed more.</li>\n </ul>\n <p>Descriptions</p>\n <p><br/></p>\n <p><br/></p>\n <p>Metal bed, 3FT single bed 90x190cm, With LED light strip and 4 drawerss</p>\n <p>This Metal single bed, measuring 90x190cm (3FT), the bed is made of a sturdy iron frame that ensures longevity and stability, which is essential for children's safety and comfort. LED light strips around the bed can be adjusted in colour and brightness to create a warm and dreamy sleeping environment for your child, which can be customised according to your own preferences, whether it's a fresh and natural green or a dreamy and romantic purple, which will make this iron bed a unique and personalised space, and there are also three charging ports thoughtfully prepared at the head of the bed, including two 2 Type-A and one Type-C, 5V / 2A. Designed with four iron drawers with pulleys under the bed, the thoughtfully designed built-in drawers offer ample space to tuck away clutter, freeing up valuable floor area and keeping your room clutter-free.</p>\n <p><br/></p>\n <p><br/></p>\n <p>Selling point\uff1a</p>\n <p>1.Iron bed slats, sturdy and durable 2.Textured solid wood colour 3.Simple single bed size: 90*190cm 4.Bedside design with storage space + dazzling colourful light strips + three charging ports 5.Four drawers under the bed, each with four universal wheels </p>\n <p>Weight &amp; Dimensions</p>\n <table>\n  <tbody>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Overall Size</td>\n    <td>207x90.5 x105cm</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Overall Product Weight</td>\n    <td>34KG</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Mattresses (Not included)</td>\n    <td>Bed: 90x190cm (Mattress thickness less than 13 cm)</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Load Capacity</td>\n    <td>158KG</td>\n   </tr>\n  </tbody>\n </table>\n <p>Features</p>\n <table>\n  <tbody>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Product name</td>\n    <td>Metal bed</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Colour</td>\n    <td>Grey</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Frame Material</td>\n    <td>Metal</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Slat Material</td>\n    <td>Metal</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Installation method:</td>\n    <td>Self-installation</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Package Number</td>\n    <td>2</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Country of Origin</td>\n    <td>China</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Tip</td>\n    <td>There are 2 parcels of this product, it is normal that these 2 parcels are not delivered at the same time, please be patient.</td>\n   </tr>\n  </tbody>\n </table>\n <p><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/af675b45-1589-4cf9-81df-e0089d0df79b.png\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/65e28e98-957c-48a4-9688-48942caf4b44.jpg\" data-key=\"1\" data-uploadossfail=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/e6123635-c665-4e0b-be61-ffcd8d0a3688.png\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/1108d1c9-d98e-4808-87b3-d3a2f81215ea.jpg\" data-key=\"2\" data-uploadossfail=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/34a8a829-305f-485b-a6d5-5e67e2508f1b.png\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/016e8c16-562b-433a-9021-54a6a0d033a9.jpg\" data-key=\"3\" data-uploadossfail=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/69cf6471-253e-41e7-a82f-8aed243a3892.png\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/2938f3b4-b341-4696-9cd6-3d49d5969a4f.jpg\" data-key=\"4\" data-uploadossfail=\"false\"/><img src=\"https